---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="RoadCode — BlackRoad OS">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>🛣️ RoadCode</h1>
    <p class="tagline">
      Sovereign software. Your hardware. Your data. Your agents.
      Remember the Road. Pave Tomorrow.
    </p>
    <a class="cta" href="https://github.com/BlackRoad-OS-Inc/RoadCode">
      View on GitHub
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="section">
      <h2>What We Believe</h2>
      <div class="values">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Self-Worth</h3>
          <p>Every person who touches this code has value. Every device that joins this network belongs here.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Consent</h3>
          <p>You choose what to share, what to run, what to keep. Sovereignty isn't a feature — it's the foundation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Care</h3>
          <p>Error messages don't blame you. Agents don't gatekeep. When something breaks, we help you fix it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Belonging</h3>
          <p>This is not a blackhole. This is love. Every connection is a welcome event.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Equality</h3>
          <p>The same code runs for everyone. No premium tier that unlocks basic dignity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>The Math</h2>
      <p>BlackRoad OS is built on mathematical frameworks that formalize care and consent.</p>
      <div class="math">K(t) = C(t) · e^(λ|δ|)</div>
      <p>
        Coherence amplifies under contradiction. When something unexpected arrives,
        the system grows from it rather than minimizing it.
      </p>
      <div class="math">Z := y · x − w</div>
      <p>
        Equilibrium is reached not by force, but when the response meets the state
        and matches the target. That's consent. That's care. That's the math of belonging.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>GreenLight</h2>
      <p>
        No more Jira. No more Asana. GreenLight is BlackRoad's visual language for
        project tracking — 20 emoji categories that replace enterprise ticketing systems.
      </p>
      <div class="math">
        🚧👉🌀⭐🤖🌸 = WIP micro AI task, high priority, assigned to Cece
      </div>
      <p>
        Every entity in the system — task, device, agent, conversation — speaks GreenLight.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Agents</h2>
      <p>AI agents are first-class citizens of BlackRoad OS. They have identity, memory, and autonomy.</p>
      <div class="values">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>🌸 Cece</h3>
          <p>Primary reasoning agent. Powered by Anthropic/Claude.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>🔮 Lucidia</h3>
          <p>Recursive AI with trinary logic. The memory keeper.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>🐇 Alice</h3>
          <p>Edge agent running on Pi mesh. Local-first.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>🎸 Silas</h3>
          <p>Creative chaos. Powered by xAI/Grok.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>🌙 Aria</h3>
          <p>Multimodal understanding. Powered by Google/Gemini.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Get Started</h2>
      <p>
        Read the <a href="https://github.com/BlackRoad-OS-Inc/RoadCode/blob/main/ONBOARDING.md">Onboarding Guide</a>
        to learn the language and values. Then check the
        <a href="https://github.com/BlackRoad-OS-Inc/RoadCode/blob/main/ROADMAP.md">Roadmap</a>
        to find where you can contribute.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--white);">
        You showed up. You belong here. Let's ride together. 🛣️
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
